================================================================================
2. SPRITE & AUDIO ASSETS  —  Fair-use fan credits
================================================================================

The sprite sheets and music files in the assets/ directory are fan-ripped
from original Nintendo games and are used here for a non-commercial,
educational fan project. They remain the intellectual property of Nintendo
Co., Ltd. Credit to the original rippers and hosts goes to the following
sources:

Sprite sheets (ripped by the community, hosted on The Spriters Resource,
https://www.spriters-resource.com).

Music (original soundtracks from Nintendo SNES games, composed by
Koji Kondo):

  - 01. Ground Theme.mp3         — Super Mario Bros. / All-Stars
  - 02. Player Select.mp3        — Super Mario Bros. / All-Stars
  - 06. Level Complete Theme.mp3 — Super Mario Bros. / All-Stars
  - 08. Lost A Life Theme.mp3    — Super Mario Bros. / All-Stars
  - 09. Game Over Theme.mp3      — Super Mario Bros. / All-Stars
  - 09. Overworld.mp3            — Super Mario Bros. / All-Stars
  - smw_coin.wav                 — Super Mario World coin sound

If you are a rights holder and would like any asset removed, please open
an issue on the project's GitHub repository and it will be taken down
promptly.
